                <pb n="1"/>
            <p>Dear Mr Morais<lb/></p>
            <p>As on other side I have<lb/> issued notices.  I saw Dr Drachman<lb/> this a.m. he will send you today<lb/> report&#44;&#45;&#45;of course it should be<lb/> made couleur de rose as much as<lb/> is consistent with truth.<lb/></p>
            <p>Am waking up boys&#45;&#45;to send delegates&#44;<lb/> Kindest regards to all<lb/> yrs H Pereira Mendes<lb/></p>
            
            <pb n="2"/>
            <p>Rev Dr S Morais<lb/></p>
            <p>My dear Sir<lb/></p>
            <p>Will you please attend<lb/> a meeting of the Advisory Board<lb/> of the Seminary next Thursday evening 8 p.m.<lb/> at Dr Kohut&#39;s 39 Beekman Place.<lb/></p>
            <p>The importance of the meeting<lb/> is evident in view of the approaching convention&#44;<lb/> which takes place Sunday next It is hoped<lb/> therefore that you will attend in order<lb/> that any final <del>recommendation</del> action<lb/> necessary may be taken.<lb/>  Yrs<lb/> H Pereira Mendes<lb/> &#91;&#63;&#93;.<lb/></p>
            </body>
    </text>
